title: Field Hockey Roundup for Thursday, Oct. 1
text:
Field Hockey Roundup for Thursday, Oct. 1 Steven Macri @StevenMacri 7:28 p.m. EDT October 1, 2015 Field hockey 1 CONNECT 3 TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Pingry 6, East Brunswick 0: Mary Pagano had three goals to lead the charge for Pingry (4-5). Josie Cummings, Jess Foy and Josie Jahng each found the back of the cage in the win. 
Voorhees 6, Franklin 0: Kathryn Roncoroni errupted for five goals and Cori Lenzinger added another score for Voorhees (8-2). Annie Weiler had four saves in goal. Read or Share this story: http://mycj.co/1FJyI9u TOP VIDEOS
